{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, we adopted a quantitative evaluation of the impact of feature representations in a biological downstream task, to guide the search for improved workflow.",
    "The evaluation is based on querying a reference collection of treatments to find biological matches in a perturbation experiment.",
    "In each evaluation, cell morphology features change to compare different strategies, while the rest of the image-based profiling workflow remains constant.",
    "Performance is measured using metrics for the quality of a ranked list of results for each query (Fig. 1G).",
    "With this evaluation framework, we conduct an extensive analysis on three publicly available Cell Painting datasets."
  ]
}